  "body": "<p>Hey, better late than never - right? Here are more photos from Craftcation as promised from <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2014/04/craftcation-wrap-up.html\">this post</a>. Photos by <a href=\"http://www.matthewwilliamphotography.com/\">Matthew William</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7a-craft14-1061.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758209426-APB2T8SJVEMLEIQ9ZWFU/7a-craft14-1061.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7b-craft14-1248.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758209507-KJ5ZF0SWSHAAMQM45HRM/7b-craft14-1248.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7c-craft14-1294.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758209980-LRMUT0FC0JFDHMFD1HYY/7c-craft14-1294.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-craft14-1062.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758210055-DCA8A1XTX9M35SA6PUS6/7d-craft14-1062.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-craftcation.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758211415-OEUMMRA9X2GU2JM1DM9O/7e-craftcation.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-craft14-1064.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758210927-KYVAR40DE575ML5P7J8I/7f-craft14-1064.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-craft14-1065.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758211482-K32Z1QH3F23NXA9QJQEW/7g-craft14-1065.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7h-craft14-1121.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758212111-LIG4867LFZ1RJ0PP3ICV/7h-craft14-1121.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7i-craft14-1400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758212155-81N3S5VGQKNZY9J1QDPA/7i-craft14-1400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7j-craft14-1401.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598758212874-705